  "text": [
    "I want to be a passenger",
    "in your car again",
    "and shut my eyes",
    "while you sit at the wheel,",
    "awake and assured",
    "in your own private world,",
    "seeing all the lines",
    "on the road ahead,",
    "down a long stretch",
    "of empty highway",
    "without any other",
    "faces in sight.",
    "I want to be a passenger",
    "in your car again",
    "and put my life back",
    "in your hands."
  ],
